<h1>Email Change Initiated</h1>

<p>
  This is a security notification to inform you that an email change request has been initiated for your MOSSLET account.
</p>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<EmailComponents.status type="info">
  <strong>🔄 Change Request Details:</strong>
  <br /> New email address: <strong>{@new_email}</strong>
  <br /> Request time: Just now<br /> Status: Awaiting confirmation
</EmailComponents.status>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<p>To complete this change, you'll need to:</p>
<ol>
  <li>📧 Check the inbox for <strong>{@new_email}</strong></li>
  <li>🔗 Click the confirmation link in the email we sent</li>
  <li>✅ Your email will be updated once confirmed</li>
</ol>

<p>
  This helps ensure that only you can change your email address and that you maintain access to your account.
</p>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<EmailComponents.status type="warning">
  <strong>⚠️ Security Alert:</strong>
  If you didn't request this email change, please secure your account immediately.
</EmailComponents.status>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<p>If this wasn't you:</p>
<ul>
  <li>🔒 Change your password immediately</li>
  <li>📧 Contact our support team at support@mosslet.com</li>
  <li>🛡️ Review your account activity and security settings</li>
</ul>

<EmailComponents.gap />

<EmailComponents.top_border>
  <EmailComponents.small_text>
    This notification was sent to your current email address to keep you informed of account changes. MOSSLET takes your privacy and security seriously.
  </EmailComponents.small_text>

  <EmailComponents.small_text>
    If you have any concerns about your account security, please contact us immediately at support@mosslet.com.
  </EmailComponents.small_text>
</EmailComponents.top_border>
